Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[scene]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're going to Mistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear they have good food and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been half a year since Armistice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that we're both still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey that's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey girl, you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your share of our war booty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you so much for giving me something so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Dear, Sergant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're nice to the trumpeter, you'll be able to hear the retreat calls well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare we get new soldiers since the draft was abolished.{YUI!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I wanted to learn music!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's not like that, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is fine! Work hard, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private second class, your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorami Kanata is my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sora No Oto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Resounding Sound -\NThe City at Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize is having a festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can only deliver you up to right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is where you have been assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's commonly known as the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be heading in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private 2nd class, Sorami Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assigned to 1121 Platoon of Trois State, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helvetia Republic Army Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished at 1320 hours!{army way of saying 13:20}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of glass and lakes, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1500 is the time to report in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direction check, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time check, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment check, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,March on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a marvellous sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow! A fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10yen 25sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what a beautiful doll{\fscx200}-{MIO!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat that got excited from the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,went shooting off in some random direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats are supposed to wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes them cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a stray cat that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, that one has a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting all involved in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with your uniform all like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank yo{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you were an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least try to evade them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this dye will come off when its dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's was part of the festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's based on a legend of Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Maidens protect the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The repairs for that are done too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filishia eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meddler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late!{TSUMUGI!!! sans eyebrows}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is soooooo late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way to pick her up!{AZUNYAN!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay let's wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a present from your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wonderful bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but I often get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, I was able to experience something wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get lost in here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very clear sound and somehow brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant-{sound and note are the same in Jap}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to die for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must have been how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:33.32,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Scene]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business to take care of, so I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost any more, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,March on, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the world before it became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the valley, in this city, a winged demon once lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon spread fire and shook the ground, causing the people to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally it stole the all the maidens in the fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and trapped them in an underground maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens did not give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and called upon each other with the golden horn given to them by the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they escaped the maze, the maidens cooperated with a very large spider and defeated the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they beheaded the demon,\Nits head violently shot out flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the rate the fire was spreading, the town above would have been burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop the erupting fire, the maidens, in turn, continued to embrace the demon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday, the villagers kept spraying water on both the blazing head and the maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a year passed, the fire was finally extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, to comfort the spirits of the maidens who saved the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the water spraying festival was celebrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new girl didn't come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, captain, it's Rio senpai!{waaaaa the Mio lookalike is named Rio!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she fits the role quite nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was correct in entrusting her with this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But that was by lotter{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so needless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being lost is fun sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because you get to see someone you didn't know before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that feeling of wanting to see her will get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound always resounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always resounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always resounds, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And will get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Maiden sleeps here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing the demon, and relieving the curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to let it awaken once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the demon have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receive it, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept my sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was received.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound resounds, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private second class, Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will you wake up all the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Telling Fortress, {//check av sync}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the 1121 platoon's station!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry to have troubled you yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't do reckless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for one bell like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why this fortress is called the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall train you as the trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Sergeant Major Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Filicia, our captain's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't talk about rank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us begin right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow the Morning Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new girl is bad.
